            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> pho broth paste </strong>to a bowl<strong> </strong>with your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>,<strong> soy sauce </strong>and<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>honey chilli sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
