            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong>,<strong> onion wedges</strong> and <strong>carrot batons</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Pour the <strong>honey chilli sauce </strong>over the top</p><p>Put the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in the oven and cook for an initial 15-17 min or until the vegetables have softened</p>",
