    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 15-17 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>trimmed green beans </strong>to the top of the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 10-12 min or until everything is tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>honey chilli chicken traybake</strong></p>",
